This paper deals with a learning algorithm for a stochastic inventory control problem, which involves optimization and decision-making. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
